==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Snooze
<hw>Snooze</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Snoozed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
